article_title: Rodgers throws 6 TD passes in romp of Bears
article_text:
Green Bay Packers wide receiver Randall Cobb reaches to haul in a touchdown catch at the end of the second quarter during the Green Bay Packers-Chicago Bears NFL football game at Lambeau Field in Green Bay, Wisconsin, Sunday, November 9, 2014. Milwaukee Journal Sentinel photo by Rick Wood/RWOOD@JOURNALSENTINEL.COM Credit: Rick Wood

The Packers (5-3) and Bears (3-5) meet for the final time this regular season at Lambeau Field tonight. Get perspectives and join the discussion as Packers beat writer Tom Silverstein provides updates of the game beginning at 7 p.m.
